WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.105
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining me again today. And Diana today, I'm so excited to have you with us.

00:00:09.106 --> 00:00:14.694
She's been so busy doing some other stuff for the ministry and doing things; I haven't been able to have her on as much.

00:00:14.695 --> 00:00:18.380
And I told her, I said, 'Tonight you are going to be on here with me.

00:00:18.381 --> 00:00:26.562
I need you.'So, I'm excited you're here. I sure love you. You know, we're going to go over some of the things.

00:00:26.563 --> 00:00:38.445
Tell everybody hi. Hi. Yeah, we're so grateful. You know, it's exciting to be in the ministry and pushing like we do.

00:00:38.446 --> 00:00:43.555
We know Jesus is coming. We have an expectation. People say, 'Brandon, what do you do?

00:00:43.556 --> 00:00:54.092
Do you really believe Jesus is coming beyond anything?'I'm telling you, we are at the last seconds of the last days.

00:00:54.093 --> 00:01:03.459
Jesus Christ is coming, ladies and gentlemen. And it's time for you to have your expectation of the manifestations and the glory of God.

00:01:03.460 --> 00:01:15.184
Get excited about what God's about to do in these last days. I'll go over a little bit of what I saw in the revival. I told you about the angels and the oil coming out of the sky.

00:01:15.185 --> 00:01:23.399
And people are like, 'Brandon, that's way over the top.'And I'm like, 'Yeah, that's exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.'God we serve.

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:34.766
But I want to talk about today, wherever you are—morning, day, or night. I want to talk about what's going on with Russia.

00:01:34.767 --> 00:01:44.133
What I feel about some of this caution that I have in the Valley of Decision that President Trump is making right now.

00:01:44.134 --> 00:01:49.902
And I want to say this: Diana and I tease around with each other about calling him Mr.

00:01:49.903 --> 00:01:53.886
Magoo and things like that. We don't mean any disrespect toward the president.

00:01:53.887 --> 00:01:59.859
We pray for him. We love our president and stand with him, but just teasing around.

00:01:59.860 --> 00:02:03.903
I would say even if I got to be his friend and hang out with him, I'd call him Mr.

00:02:03.904 --> 00:02:11.756
Magoo because in the natural, he always seems to look like he's about to go off a cliff, but God saves him and he wins the case.

00:02:11.757 --> 00:02:16.480
Mr. Magoo was always victorious. So, it wasn't that Mr. Magoo was an idiot; Mr.

00:02:16.481 --> 00:02:21.832
Magoo won. And you're always like, 'How did that happen?'It was just the hand of God.

00:02:21.833 --> 00:02:36.905
This is how you look at some of the things when you watch him and you're going, 'I don't know, is this going to turn out okay?'But God. And that's why I say Mr. Magoo was one of those ones.

00:02:36.906 --> 00:02:51.874
You watched him on the cartoon whenever we were growing up and he was walking on the steel beam and it went through the window and he walked out on the other side, but he never got hurt and you're going, 'That was pretty cool.'And so that's why we laugh.

00:02:51.875 --> 00:02:58.443
We call this lots of prayer. So we know that Mr. Magoo is going to turn out okay.

00:02:58.444 --> 00:03:11.476
And so we're just not going to worry about him. Why is he talking to Russia right now? What's he doing? Mr. Magoo, don't talk to Russia.

00:03:11.477 --> 00:03:24.352
I don't mean disrespect, but I'm just saying it made me think of it a lot whenever I hear these articles. And so I reached out to Diana and I said, 'You know what?

00:03:24.353 --> 00:03:40.749
What do you think about what's going on?'She had told me, she said, 'This is what my daddy prophesied concerning Russia.'And I'll play that clip in just a second, but I want to go over what the Lord showed us.

00:03:40.750 --> 00:03:47.871
Probably back—I don't know, Braden can show you a little clip of it—but I saw a Jason Bourne type of experience.

00:03:47.873 --> 00:03:52.399
I saw Zelensky snorting coke and he had prostitutes around him.

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:59.319
I saw that he had a hundred million in $100 bills and they were on a plane and he was going to flee.

00:03:59.320 --> 00:04:09.488
But there was a plan in the days ahead with Russia and America to remove him like a Jason Bourne experience.

00:04:09.489 --> 00:04:15.343
So I saw a Jason Bourne kind of a decision being made when this happened.

00:04:15.344 --> 00:04:47.599
I saw Russia get half of Ukraine all the way up to Kyiv and they brought in a new government that was pro-Russia, pro-Ukraine, and it brought peace to the area because the puppet was being manipulated by the EU and Macron, and he was looking with his Pinocchio nose towards Macron asking, 'What should we do?

00:04:47.600 --> 00:05:11.886
What should we do?'So, I thought this was kind of interesting because whenever I had the visitation with the Lord and He was here in the vision, I saw a Russian man on his belly with a black stocking hat and black pants, black everything.

00:05:11.887 --> 00:05:20.529
So then I give that word of what I heard the Lord say. And then he goes and becomes buddies with Russia.

00:05:20.530 --> 00:05:26.867
Let's bring our dollar together again. Look at this article right here.

00:05:26.868 --> 00:05:34.440
Now you see what Russia is saying today, that they want to join up with America and the dollar and they're wanting to do...

00:05:34.441 --> 00:05:45.427
so what is happening with the BRICS if they do that? Are they abandoning the BRICS system when they said, 'We'll help Cuba out'with the next one I saw right here?

00:05:45.428 --> 00:05:51.503
You can see that. So Cuba and Russia are wanting to do oil agreements and all that.

00:05:51.504 --> 00:05:56.599
So what's going on with all this? Is this just a smoke screen?

00:05:56.600 --> 00:06:12.759
Because I saw the Tasmanian looking devil spinning around Putin creating major war with this new weapon over Warsaw that has never been used before.

00:06:12.760 --> 00:06:30.442
And he had his hands like this looking at his cards and he said, 'I just have to buy the time to get through your presidency and then I'll make my move,'because he was looking for weaker leadership. So he was looking at his poker cards.

00:06:30.443 --> 00:06:49.648
He had a poker face, as you saw in the cartoon that we made, and he was trying to figure out what his best move was to win the game because he wants to win all of these areas back—what was the former Soviet Union and all that back then.

00:06:49.649 --> 00:07:05.435
So we see this stuff. What's happening right now with his decision? Is he being sneaky? I believe he is.

00:07:05.436 --> 00:07:17.239
I want you to hear this word from Kim Clement back—I don't even know, she didn't tell me the date of this. It's a 47-second word.

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:31.079
'The other thing the Lord said to me today, Jacob,'he said, 'Kim, tell my people to keep their eye on Russia because there's a huge deception that is taking place and is yet to unveil and where people will even embrace it.

00:07:31.080 --> 00:07:42.306
I'm not sure exactly what it is, but I saw this hand coming out of Russia and this hand being extended out to the Christian people and to the Jews as if it were a friend.

00:07:42.307 --> 00:07:47.672
It is not a friend. Russia is not a friend to the Jews and not a friend to the Christians.

00:07:47.673 --> 00:07:54.134
I'm not speaking about the people of Russia. I'm talking about the administration and the leaders. I saw deception coming out of Russia.

00:07:54.135 --> 00:08:09.599
I saw a hand coming out as if to shake and then as the hand was shaken by purple robes and garments of religion, I saw the hand raised up and then smashing them on the neck.'So I think that's interesting.

00:08:09.600 --> 00:08:26.239
I believe the hand he's talking about is all of the persecution that's coming to the church, persecution coming to the Jews, all the things that I've seen, the antisemitism, the things that are about to erupt on another level.

00:08:26.240 --> 00:08:37.319
But like I said, I know he flowed in the prophetic. I see visions and I believe visions change through prayer. Prayer changes things.

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:44.747
Now, I believe a vision is a lot different than a prophetic 'Thus saith the Lord.'There's a lot of people that disagree with me.

00:08:44.748 --> 00:08:50.028
I don't care what you really believe. It's whatever you feel the Lord's leading you.

00:08:50.029 --> 00:08:55.086
That's just what I feel. I see a lot of visions and the Lord shows me these things through prayer.

00:08:55.087 --> 00:09:08.865
He said, 'Your job is to have a prayer channel and tell people what's coming and you'll change things through prayer.'And that's why I've always looked at it as a watchman telling people.

00:09:08.866 --> 00:09:22.679
Now, is it prophetic? I said it has a prophetic lens. It's different in my opinion, but I yield to the anointing of the prophet.

00:09:22.680 --> 00:09:30.114
We hear all this stuff going on. We see these major things taking place. I thought it was really interesting.

00:09:30.115 --> 00:10:01.476
Diana said, 'Did you notice the people on Twitter talking about the three electric poles at the Super Bowl that looked like Bunny was on the one in the middle with the cross, and it looked like he was being like Jesus?'I wondered a lot about what the satanic significance was behind it because the Lord said there was great satanic significance behind the Super Bowl halftime show.

00:10:01.477 --> 00:10:06.735
Well, we know there's a lot of Jezebels running around and dancing and acting stupid.

00:10:06.736 --> 00:10:17.022
But what we saw with the guy that used to be the devil worshipper that got born again was directly communicating to the devil.

00:10:17.023 --> 00:10:25.159
He made a video talking about how demonic the Super Bowl halftime show was.

00:10:25.160 --> 00:10:27.610
Now, I didn't watch all of it, but I think it was interesting.

00:10:27.611 --> 00:10:34.152
I believe his name is John Ramirez or something like that. I don't remember; Braden can put it in there below.

00:10:34.153 --> 00:10:41.095
I don't know much about this man, but I thought it was interesting because he said that there was a lot of satanic things about the Super Bowl halftime show.

00:10:41.096 --> 00:10:48.116
Now, I didn't watch it. It was trash. And so anytime you have a bunch of hussies running around there, I protect and honor my wife.

00:10:48.117 --> 00:11:03.298
I'm going to look down at the ground; it was bad. It's embarrassing the kind of trash they try to feed us on the internet or on TV.

00:11:03.299 --> 00:11:18.319
Our youth kids were having youth things, and our church was having a Super Bowl party—I don't even know what they did—and how embarrassing that was with the people of the church, having anyone see some of the things that were shown during that.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:24.597
I'm just telling you all, we're in a time like never before where the dark is getting darker, but the light is getting lighter.

00:11:24.598 --> 00:11:32.313
Now, going over those prophetic words, going over what the Lord has showed us about the Mabee Center and getting excited about it.

00:11:32.314 --> 00:11:42.599
But there is darkness, and I feel great caution about this valley of decision and what's happening with Trump right now.

00:11:42.600 --> 00:11:47.877
I said great anti-Semitism would come out in the days ahead. Why?

00:11:47.878 --> 00:11:58.615
Because I believe Israel will probably act alone against Iran. Maybe they will, and we'll back them.

00:11:58.616 --> 00:12:14.319
Why would there be so much anti-Semitism across the world that the Jewish community would uproot and want to move back home because they felt their lives were in danger being a Jew in New York or wherever?

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:18.723
There's something that's going to trigger this; the Lord is warning of this.

00:12:18.724 --> 00:12:47.159
The other part—now I was waking up, and in between being awake and asleep, I heard this: I told you there would be black swan false flag events that would bring attention back to ABC, NBC, CBS, CNN to give them credibility, trying to get credibility back to them, to get a foothold to get you to feel sorry for them and want to be watching them again.

00:12:47.160 --> 00:13:01.999
I'll say that again. They are going to try to cause a distraction to get you to look over here because they're losing their audience.

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:20.723
And the Lord said, 'Watch for major events in the days ahead that will cause you to look more to MSNBC, ABC, CBS, CNN.'What's happened in the last couple of days?

00:13:20.724 --> 00:13:31.519
Now, I'm not trying to be disrespectful toward the lady who got kidnapped—I'm not at all—but I want you to be smarter.

00:13:31.520 --> 00:13:41.759
Think about this. The lady, the FBI, all this, it's all about her family and the network that she works for.

00:13:41.760 --> 00:13:49.895
What happened with this? Is there more to this? Does that make sense what I'm trying to tell you all?

00:13:49.896 --> 00:14:00.910
Is this the event that draws people back over there to click on them instead of watching social media as much to give ABC, NBC, CBS more of a foothold?

00:14:00.911 --> 00:14:06.811
A little bit of something, then a little bit more, to get them more credibility.

00:14:06.812 --> 00:14:12.239
You know what? Because you start to feel sorry for the individual.

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:17.279
You start because we're sympathetic. Oh, the 85-year-old woman.

00:14:17.280 --> 00:14:27.199
It's really sad. Her mom and everybody watches. But then you have a personal connection.

00:14:27.200 --> 00:14:37.929
You don't even know her, but a lot of people will get personal connections through stories and through social media when you don't even know who these people are through Erica, through all this different stuff.

00:14:37.930 --> 00:14:44.672
And then you have scandals about Erica on there, and they're talking about all this stuff. I just stay out of all the stuff. I don't care.

00:14:44.673 --> 00:14:55.825
People send me something, 'Hey Diana, you need to read it.'And I told her, 'Diana, we've got to get more filtering our filter.'Does that make sense?

00:14:55.826 --> 00:15:05.675
But I'm trying to tell you what I'm hearing. Remember the events to get back this over here, a sleight of hand.

00:15:05.676 --> 00:15:13.439
The enemy is going to try to do this somehow. And I thought, what would ever make a people want to watch them ever again?

00:15:13.440 --> 00:15:29.239
How will they do that subtly? Another 9/11 event? I don't know. What makes them become the victim?

00:15:29.240 --> 00:15:37.439
What makes the American people feel sorry for them a little bit? Is it one thing or is it multiple things?

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:51.179
But the Lord said it was coming because alternative media like Alex Jones and Benny Johnson and some of these others are drawing so much attraction.

00:15:51.180 --> 00:15:54.814
Their channels are exploding—six million views, all this stuff.

00:15:54.815 --> 00:16:05.836
And so I went back and I was looking: what's the average view count through Google for some of these TV networks like Christian television?

00:16:05.837 --> 00:16:18.072
And they said an average view count on their whole channel for a day watching them speak was only 150,000. Not even over a million.

00:16:18.072 --> 00:16:26.739
And I won't tell you who that was, but I saw a Christian organization; their main thing was 150,000 on their TV a day.

00:16:26.740 --> 00:16:34.159
And they have millions of dollars of overhead. I thought that surely that can't be right.

00:16:34.160 --> 00:16:45.796
But when you look at what they say about how much in a day CNN and some of these other places get, it's only a couple million. They're losing their audience.

00:16:45.797 --> 00:16:55.199
But when you look at Benny Johnson's video count and the subscribers and the views he gets on a video, it's by the millions.

00:16:55.200 --> 00:17:01.767
Alex Jones by the millions. They're pulling from that pool.

00:17:01.768 --> 00:17:05.186
So how do they bring back those people? And that's what I'm trying to say.

00:17:05.187 --> 00:17:22.438
The Lord said because what they want to do in the days ahead is to get a foothold in the media, a foothold in the food, a foothold in the politics—a foothold because they have to get you to believe and think they're credible again because they've lost their credibility.

00:17:22.439 --> 00:17:30.930
And people and the world, not just the body of Christ, are saying, 'We're done.'So we're seeing it. Let's see what happens in the days ahead.

00:17:30.931 --> 00:17:50.999
The Lord said, 'Watch 2026, 2027, and 2028.'And they will say there will be more pressure on YouTube to censor what these big YouTube platforms and news media stations will be able to say because they'll take away their AdSense and things like that.

00:17:51.000 --> 00:17:56.559
They'll be able to say, 'Listen, you're going to say what we want you to say on your platform or we're taking this away from you.'And that's what I saw happening.

00:17:56.560 --> 00:18:04.935
So I just wanted to go over that because those are the things I'm seeing. This is big.

00:18:04.936 --> 00:18:16.405
There's a lot, but I haven't wanted to be quick in just releasing videos about some of this stuff because I feel it; there's a changing of the tide.

00:18:16.406 --> 00:18:20.159
There's something happening in this valley of decision right now.

00:18:20.160 --> 00:18:31.479
There are some major decisions being made as Benjamin came to the White House yesterday or the day before yesterday.

00:18:31.480 --> 00:18:38.239
Folks, this is what I saw. This is what the Lord warned us about.

00:18:38.240 --> 00:18:50.239
We're here; it's time to wake up. What will come in 2026? What will the rest of it be like? What will we see within these 250 years?

00:18:50.240 --> 00:19:00.954
And I told you about Red Dawn experiences and shakings in our nation—shaking in Europe, the Euro, the plagues, and the things with the biolab.

00:19:00.955 --> 00:19:07.273
All the things that a biolab just got busted and he was experimenting with mice and all this stuff.

00:19:07.274 --> 00:19:16.959
I was like, "This is not a Batman movie. This is real-life stuff.

00:19:16.960 --> 00:19:20.620
This isn't watching Spider-Man and seeing who the new villain is.

00:19:20.621 --> 00:19:25.506
This is real stuff. Who's Professor Xavier or whoever?"I don't know.

00:19:25.507 --> 00:19:31.211
You see some of these Superman movies with the bad guys and you go, "What is going on?

00:19:31.212 --> 00:19:41.010
This is real-life superhero weirdness."I just try to go over it.

00:19:41.011 --> 00:19:45.938
We love every single one of you and we're so thankful that you're here.

00:19:45.939 --> 00:19:55.449
Like I said, I'm just kind of watching. I feel a caution. I feel that major storm on the East Coast.

00:19:55.450 --> 00:20:03.017
I told you I saw biological weapons being taken from Russia to put into Cuba. Is this the opportunity where they're doing that?

00:20:03.018 --> 00:20:08.382
And they were putting them underground, saying "storm here."It was in the middle of the night—the trafficking and the things.

00:20:08.383 --> 00:20:18.728
And here we see Venezuela and all this stuff going on. Is this all coming about where you let your guard down?

00:20:18.729 --> 00:20:24.415
President Trump, be careful who you trust. Be careful who you let into your inner circle.

00:20:24.416 --> 00:20:36.239
Be careful who extends an olive branch of peace to you, saying, "Hey, we want to be your friend all of a sudden,"when they were your worst enemy.

00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:44.439
Remember who is in your inner circle and who you're trusting. Do not trust so easily.

00:20:44.440 --> 00:20:53.614
Be watchful over who's in your inner circle and take no counsel from the ungodly.

00:20:53.615 --> 00:21:03.319
It's so important because all it takes is one bad decision to cause the house of cards to fall.

00:21:03.320 --> 00:21:12.599
China and Taiwan—all this major stuff. Let's pray and take communion.

00:21:12.600 --> 00:21:19.057
This is my favorite part. Every time I talk, I try to keep it as short as I can.

00:21:19.058 --> 00:21:33.879
So, Father, we just lift up this body before You. We're so thankful for this time of prayer and just seeking You, God. We're so thankful for where we are in these end times.

00:21:33.880 --> 00:21:50.981
I truly believe we're at that point like You said back in September—the point of no return where we're about to see an acceleration of things that's going to be shock and awe.

00:21:50.982 --> 00:21:58.771
Lord, I'm so grateful. I don't want to look at it and say life is bad. Lord, we're ready to get out of here.

00:21:58.772 --> 00:22:05.317
I'm just looking forward to being with You, not by death but by the rapture of the church.

00:22:05.318 --> 00:22:12.079
I'm so thankful, Father, that You are coming back and we'll be reunited with all our loved ones.

00:22:12.080 --> 00:22:21.492
It's just a glorious day. Oh, what a day of rejoicing that will be when we all get to heaven.

00:22:21.493 --> 00:22:34.839
We'll sing and shout the victory. Isn't that wonderful? It's going to be exciting.

00:22:34.840 --> 00:22:47.279
Everything we've ever believed for will be complete within our glorified bodies.

00:22:47.280 --> 00:22:58.198
We'll be standing before our King. Jesus Christ is coming; I just look forward to it.

00:22:58.199 --> 00:23:04.657
We take this body and thank You, Lord, for this time when everyone is focused on love.

00:23:04.658 --> 00:23:10.719
They say we focus on Cupid and all that stuff, but no, I just love my wife.

00:23:10.720 --> 00:23:21.038
We have an extra day of just loving each other—an extra day of being on a honeymoon.

00:23:21.039 --> 00:23:27.999
I think it's a good time to reflect and rekindle the fire in your marriage.

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:35.759
You don't have to believe in all the weirdness. We just love each other, and it's a good day to love on your wife.

00:23:35.760 --> 00:23:49.010
Any day is a good day to love on your wife, but especially on Valentine's Day, try to be extra special.

00:23:49.011 --> 00:24:04.119
I think it's always good to sow love into the marriage and into the person who has given their life to you and given you children.

00:24:04.120 --> 00:24:10.194
Does that make sense? It's important. I think men don't need to be a fuddy-duddy.

00:24:10.195 --> 00:24:18.060
Be fun. Have fun. Be spontaneous. Love your spouse. Love your wives.

00:24:18.061 --> 00:24:22.519
Love your husbands. Pray with each other and honor each other.

00:24:22.520 --> 00:24:26.700
I really truly believe I can always feel when there's a flow in the spirit.

00:24:26.701 --> 00:24:29.602
I always say, "Okay, Diana, we've got to pray more together.

00:24:29.603 --> 00:24:35.563
We've got to read more together."You can feel it when you're in a covenant relationship and you're pushing together.

00:24:35.564 --> 00:24:56.839
For where two or three are gathered together in my name, there I am in the midst of them—Matthew 18:20.

00:24:56.840 --> 00:25:01.308
All glory to God. I believe that's what happens when you pray with your spouse.

00:25:01.309 --> 00:25:07.702
If you say, "I don't have anybody,"well, we'll be your two. Diana and I will agree with you.

00:25:07.703 --> 00:25:16.419
If you're single, we'll agree with you. That's why we're here—praying with you to agree with you.

00:25:16.420 --> 00:25:25.599
If you're a single mother or a single father and don't have anybody to agree with, Diana and I will agree with you.

00:25:25.600 --> 00:25:30.714
We pray and touch and agree, saying, "Whatever things are bound on earth are bound in heaven.

00:25:30.715 --> 00:25:38.950
Whatever things are loosed on earth are loosed in heaven."We believe in the power of covenant and prayer.

00:25:38.951 --> 00:25:55.599
Whenever we agree, anything can be done. Two, three, four, or five agreeing—I believe with all my heart that many hands make light work.

00:25:55.600 --> 00:26:02.314
And so that's where we are in these end times—believing together as believers standing as a family.

00:26:02.315 --> 00:26:07.519
That's why we say "Good morning, family."We believe it. We are the body of Christ.

00:26:07.520 --> 00:26:16.835
People say, "I'm Catholic."I love the Catholics. Come on over here. We love the Church of Christ. We want the Baptists.

00:26:16.836 --> 00:26:21.511
We're not just about being charismatic here; we want the body of Christ.

00:26:21.512 --> 00:26:29.959
Now, you say, "Brandon, you say certain things."Well, yes, because I believe certain things, but I'm just saying that out of love.

00:26:29.960 --> 00:26:38.650
We can agree to disagree. I don't always agree with my extended family. You don't have to agree with everybody.

00:26:38.651 --> 00:26:50.598
I have aunts that believe in the whole tribulation and things like that, and I agree to disagree, but I still love them.

00:26:50.599 --> 00:26:56.079
It's amazing when you can just love each other in spite of differences.

00:26:56.080 --> 00:27:01.153
We don't have to be mean. You don't have to be a "Sister Clipboard"and pick on people.

00:27:01.154 --> 00:27:06.072
Just say, "Hey, we love you. We don't have to agree on everything.

00:27:06.072 --> 00:27:12.516
